Subject: Re: [T2] Tranny to engine bolt 78 engine

Snoopy

Usually this indicates you previously had the 002 bellhousing, that uses
the SR17 starter
and you are installing a 091 bellhousing that takes the longer bolts and
uses the SR87 starter for the 228mm flywheel.

You better make sure your starter is going to engage your flywheel.


